@everyone With Kole making much progress on the website, we are now able to start putting up a shiny showcase to show off our team shinies!! If you would like your shinies to be showcased, please create a forum post at your earliest convenience (you don't have to do them all at the same time if it is tedious for you) in <#1371610890427826278> with a screenshot of your shiny and the following information:
- Date caught
- Location caught/hatched
- OT # ___
- Encounters (how many it took)
- Encounter method (single, horde, egg, etc)
- Phases (if applicable)
- Any special notes you want added 

Any of the previous information that isn't put with your showcase will result in it not being shown on your shiny's information.
Please only submit shinies that are your OT.
This is not a requirement. This is only if you'd like us to showcase your shinies in our team website and have them added to our shiny dex completion. 
Please be patient with them being added. This will take time to get everyone's on the website.
